e]]\n|-\n!colspan=8| LMGTE Pro (11 entries)\n|-\n|align=center| 51\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[AF Corse]]\n| [[Ferrari 488 GTE#Ferrari 488 GTE EVO|Ferrari 488 GTE Evo]]\n| {{Michelin}}\n|align=center| '''<span style=\"padding:1px 4px; color:white; background-color:green;\">WEC</span>'''\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[James Calado]]\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Alessandro Pier Guidi]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Daniel Serra]]\n|-\n|align=center| 63\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Pratt & Miller|Corvette Racing]]\n| [[Chevrolet Corvette (C8)|Chevrolet Corvette C8.R]]\n| {{Michelin}}\n|align=center| '''<span style=\"padding:1px 4px; color:white; background-color:red\">WTSC</span>'''\n| {{flagicon|NLD}} [[Nicky Catsburg]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Antonio Garc\u00eda (racing driver)|Antonio Garc\u00eda]]\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Jordan Taylor (racing driver)|Jordan Taylor]]\n|-\n|align=center| 64\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Pratt & Miller|Corvette Racing]]\n| [[Chevrolet Corvette (C8)|Chevrolet Corvette C8.R]]\n| {{Michelin}}\n|align=center| '''<span style=\"padding:1px 4px; color:white; background-color:red\">WTSC</span>'''\n| {{flagicon|CHE}} [[Marcel F\u00e4ssler (racing driver)|Marcel F\u00e4ssler]]\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Oliver Gavin]]\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Tommy Milner]]\n|-\n|align=center| 71\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[AF Corse]]\n| [[Ferrari 488 GTE#Ferrari 488 GTE EVO|Ferrari 488 GTE Evo]]\n| {{Michelin}}\n|align=center| '''<span style=\"padding:1px 4px; color:white; background-color:green;\">WEC</span>'''\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Sam Bird]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Miguel Molina (racing driver)|Miguel Molina]]\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Davide Rigon]]\n|-\n|align=center| 82\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Risi Competizione]]\n| [[Ferrari 488 GTE#Ferrari 488 GTE EVO|Ferrari 488 GTE Evo]]\n| {{Michelin}}\n|align=center| '''<span style=\"padding:1px 4px; color:white; background-color:red\">WTSC</span>'''\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[S\u00e9bastien Bourdais]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Olivier Pla]]\n| {{flagicon image|Flag of None.svg}} TBA\n|-\n|ali